decision_conditions:
CONDITION:   Details and samples of the facing materials shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority before any superstructure work is commenced on site. The samples and details shall include:
a)	render;
b)	glass blocks;
c)	canopies;
d)	balustrading and railing treatment (including sections); 

The development shall be carried out strictly in accordance with the details so approved, maintained as such thereafter and no change there from shall take place without the prior written consent of the Local Planning Authority. 

REASON:  To ensure that the Authority may be satisfied with the external appearance of the building.
